#Simple Multi-page Website

This is a beginner-friendly multi-pages website built using HTML and CSS.
It includes a Home, About, and Contact Page.

---

## Project Structure

```

simple-website/
|
|___index.html
|___about.html
|___contact.html
|___style.scc 
|___README.md
```

## Pages

-**index.html** -> Home Page 
-**about.html** -> About Page 
-**contact.html** -> Contact Page 

All pages are connected using a simple navigation bar 

---

## Features

-Clean and simple design
-Navigation bar on all pages
-Responsive layout
-Separate CSS friendly

## Technologies used

-HTML5 
-CSS 

--- 
## Notes  

-Make sure your home page file is named **index.html** 
-All files must be in the root folder(not inside another folder)

